Puff pastry
Almond milk
Sesame seeds





Use one portion of base mix. Add herbs, spices and bread and mix together. Add oil and stir thoroughly.
Put mince onto pastry and roll. Top with almond milk and sesame seeds Cook in oven at 200C for 25 mins (time will depend on oven heat and roll size).













eggplant
onion
garlic
oil
beans (2x cans)





Slice eggplant and rub with salt. Wait 20 mins.
Finely dice eggplant, onion and garlic.
Brown onion, then add eggplant and allow to soften. Then add garlic.
Mince beans into a smoothish paste. Add to the onion/eggplant mixture. Add additional oil if required.













Mushrooms (200g)
Eggplant
Onion
Garlic
Chilli
Oil
Butter





Slice eggplant and rub with salt. Wait 30 mins.
In separate batches, blend mushrooms, eggplant, onion, garlic and chilli in a blender.
Brown onion in oil. Add butter and salt, once melted add mushrooms and allow to brown.

